snippet.title: "It's Over" AH Faces 5 Years In Prison After Johnny Depp Wins Case...?!
snippet.description:
"It's Over"  AH Faces 5 Years After Lying In Court And Loosing The Case...?!
When it comes to Johnny Depp, it seems as though a lot has been going against him as of late. Not the least of which is the court situation with his ex-wife Amber Heard. But she has gone and blasted Johnny Depp every which way she can to try and convince people that he  her during their one-year marriage. But Johnny has maintained his innocence and fought back...and yet has lost many things during that time. Including a Libel case in the UK. But at last, a major victory has come forth, and it could turn things around! Allow us to break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!
